title: How To Lose Weight During the Holidays, Part 2
itunes:title: How To Lose Weight During the Holidays, Part 2
description:
Get the Free Course here:
https://phit.click/freecourse

 

Are you worried what people will think of you? With Christmas parties and Thanksgiving coming it's easy to start worrying other people will think things like..."She's put on weight." "What happened to that diet she was on?" If so, this podcast will help you figure out why we think these things. And, we will help you figure out how to start thinking new things.
